reviews.text: A regular small cha-can-ting. Tried it out with an item off from the daily special menu. Presentation and taste are slightly disappointing, but I understand their constraints. For a few hkd more the local fast food chains could easily bulldoze over such business with their economies of scale. It is sad that gradually these old styled cha-can-tings will disappear in the competition.
